Ever wondered how it's like to live inside a giant brick, and shoot the hell out of your enemies? Well now you can blow one up too! In this exciting map made by LoBo, and inspiration by 3kliksphilip and his mad awesome mapping skills, de_Brik was thought of back a few days after fy_blok was created, it was the map that inspired this ^^. Also take note that this is my first map, so be easy.
